Class Description
Controller
A class that handles input and output for the entire Tuition Manager GUI.
Date
A class that stores a date based off of an input string in mm/dd/yyyy format.
International
A class that stores information about an international student.
Main
A launcher class to initialize and create the Tuition Manager GUI.
Major
Creates a collection of constant Major data types.
NonResident
A class that stores information about a non-resident student.
Profile
A class that stores information about a student's profile.
Resident
A class that stores information about a resident student.
Roster
Collects and manages Student objects in roster array.
Student
A class that stores information about a student.
TriState
A class that stores information about a student from the tri-state area.
